475
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:31,759
(from now on,)

476
00:30:32,480 --> 00:30:33,720
(I am simply He Yan.)

477
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,559
(In this vast world,)

478
00:30:37,359 --> 00:30:39,000
(I'm no longer anyone's substitute.)

479
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:44,119
(He Rufei stole my title
as General Feihong,)

480
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:46,759
(tried to kill me, and ruined my name.)

481
00:30:47,599 --> 00:30:49,200
(I won't let him off.)

482
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:54,359
(I will return to the army)

483
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:56,000
